<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/676">إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ </a>مِثْلَهُ،<span class="c5"> وَزَادَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَنْ كَانَ يُؤْمِنُ بِاللهِ وَالْيَوْمِ الْآخِرِ فَلْيَقُلْ خَيْرًا أَوْ لِيَصْمُتْ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>